Welcome to
Tin Building
A unique market and Food hall inspired by jean-georges world travels, located in new york city at the Historic Seaport.
Tin Building Hours of Operation
Sunday - Thursday8:00am - 10:00pm
Friday & Saturday8:00am - 10:30pm

Restaurants & Bars

Enjoy classic favorites and new culinary adventures at Tin Buildings 12 dining concepts featuring global cuisine, thoughtfully created dishes, and sustainable, organic, and locally-sourced ingredients. Explore fine dining, quick bites, and takeout & delivery.
